    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47228</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_050_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>『なりきり士』の力って
不思議だけど、すごいね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I admit that however weird it sounds that Roleplayer power really is incredible.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47340</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_050_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>初めはわたしも戸惑いました。
いつもと全然違う自分になって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>At first it was really weird, honestly, what with always turning into things I'm not.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47436</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_050_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、それがだんだん
気持ちよくなってきて</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But I've started to really like it! It's quite fun!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47596</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_050_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;の恍惚の表情は、何度見てもたまらんだー∀
それも含めて『なりきり士』の、すんばらしいところだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt;'s face when casting healing spells is so cute! I can't get enough out of it! With so many clothes, the Roleplayer powers have endless possibilities!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47704</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_050_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私も思いきって、
いつもと違う自分に変身したいです……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I-if I'm allowed to say, I'd like to be something other than myself once in a while.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47828</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_050_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それじゃあ、甘栗を食べるといいよ、
ヘンシン（天津）だけに……なんて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So, let's say you wore an insect suit...You'd BEE something other than yourself once in a while!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47964</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_050_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……くだらねぇだ、ひらひらマント野郎。
そしだら、ミーたまも着替えてみるだか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That sucked, Mister Mantle pushover. But I DO agree Miss &lt;Mint&gt;y should change clothes...together with me...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48040</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_050_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やめろ、このエロダンス！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stop it, you horny piece of wood!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48144</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_050_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>む、無理じゃないかな？
ほら、サイズが合わないしさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, it's not like switching clothes is impossible! As long as the sizes match---</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48260</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_050_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……そう、ですよね……
&lt;Mint&gt;さんの胸のサイズじゃ私の衣装は……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Oh that's right... I can't wear &lt;Mint&gt;'s clothes because I could never fill that chest...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48364</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_050_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あの……普通に体のサイズの話かと
思うのですが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Um... I-I'm pretty sure &lt;Cless&gt; meant body size...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
